Creating the blog home page
We now have enough tools that we can create the home page. Let‚Äôs create a new Python file and write out our simple view to list the articles in our blog.


blog-system/main.py

from fasthtml.common import *
import pathlib

app, rt = fast_app()

@rt("/")
def get():
    fnames = pathlib.Path("posts").rglob("*.md")
    items = [Li(A(fname, href=fname)) for fname in fnames]    
    return Titled("My Blog",
        Ul(*items)
    ) 

serve()


for p in posts.ls(): p.unlink()
